= Introduction =

As stable versions are finalized, the code is tagged. A standard checkout will get the latest development code. If you prefer a prior version, you can check that out be referencing its saved tag.


= Tagged Versions =

The project `nairn-mpm-fea` was first imported to `GoogleCode.com` in December 2009. The first version finalized is being tagged now.
